FlyTo Lander
Copyright 2026 MingYuan Tech Studio

This product includes software developed by MingYuan Tech Studio
(https://github.com/MingYuan-Tech).

FlyTo Lander is the Android-side helper application of FlyTo, a macOS GPS
location simulation tool. It receives broadcasts from the FlyTo macOS app
via adb and feeds simulated coordinates into the Android system through
LocationManager's Test Provider API.

